<script>\n    var playerContainers = document.querySelectorAll('.has_player');\n\n    // Only show nav when scrolled almost beyond hero (height 50% of page width minus nav height)\n    function handleStickyHeader() {\n        var bodyScrollTop = document.documentElement.scrollTop || document.body.scrollTop;\n        var heroHeight = document.querySelector('.hero').offsetHeight;\n        var header = document.querySelector('#header');\n\n        if (bodyScrollTop > (heroHeight - 79)) {\n            header.classList.add('header--fixed');\n            header.classList.remove('header--static');\n        }\n        else {\n            header.classList.remove('header--fixed');\n            header.classList.add('header--static');\n        }\n    }\n\n    function isElementVisible(el) {\n        var elRect = el.getBoundingClientRect();\n        var elTopRelative = window.innerHeight - elRect.top;\n        var elBottomRelative = window.innerHeight - elRect.bottom;\n\n        return (elTopRelative > 0 && elTopRelative < window.innerHeight) ||\n            (elBottomRelative > 0 && elBottomRelative < window.innerHeight);\n    }\n\n    function playOrPauseVisiblePlayers(forcePause) {\n        if (false) {\n            return;\n        }\n\n        for (var i = 0; i < playerContainers.length; i++) {\n            var container = playerContainers[i];\n            var player = PlayerManager.getPlayer(container);\n            var isPlayerVisible = isElementVisible(container);\n            var isPaused = player.paused;\n\n            // Force pause all playing players\n            if (forcePause && !isPaused) {\n                player.pause();\n                continue;\n            }\n\n            // Play visible players and pause off-screen players\n            if (isPaused && isPlayerVisible) {\n                player.play();\n            }\n            else if (!isPaused && !isPlayerVisible) {\n                player.pause();\n            }\n        };\n    }\n\n    function debounce(func, wait, immediate) {\n        var timeout;\n        return function() {\n            var context = this, args = arguments;\n            var later = function() {\n                timeout = null;\n                if (!immediate) func.apply(context, args);\n            };\n            var callNow = immediate && !timeout;\n            clearTimeout(timeout);\n            timeout = setTimeout(later, wait);\n            if (callNow) func.apply(context, args);\n        };\n    };\n\n    window.addEventListener('scroll', debounce(function(e) {\n        handleStickyHeader();\n        playOrPauseVisiblePlayers();\n    }, 20));\n\n    // @todo play visible videos on load! have to wait for players to set up\n\n    window.addEventListener('load', function() {\n        listenForEmail();\n        handleStickyHeader();\n\n        var mobileToggleOpen = document.querySelector('.feature_section_open');\n        if (mobileToggleOpen) {\n            mobileToggleOpen.addEventListener('click', toggleFeatureList);\n            document.querySelector('.feature_section_close').addEventListener('click', toggleFeatureList);\n        }\n    });\n\n    function listenForEmail() {\n        var form = document.querySelector('.email_form');\n        form.addEventListener('submit', submitEmailAddress);\n    }\n\n    function resetEmailErrorStatus(input) {\n        var input = document.querySelector('.email_input');\n        input.classList.remove('iris_input--error');\n        input.removeEventListener('change', resetEmailErrorStatus);\n        input.removeEventListener('keyup', resetEmailErrorStatus);\n    };\n\n    function emailSubmissionError() {\n        var input = document.querySelector('.email_input');\n        var submit = document.querySelector('.email_submit');\n\n        submit.innerText = submit.getAttribute('data-original-text');\n        submit.removeAttribute('disabled');\n        input.classList.add('iris_input--error');\n\n        input.addEventListener('change', resetEmailErrorStatus);\n        input.addEventListener('keyup', resetEmailErrorStatus);\n    }\n\n    function submitEmailAddress(e) {\n        e.preventDefault();\n        e.stopPropagation();\n\n        var input = document.querySelector('.email_input');\n        var submit = document.querySelector('.email_submit');\n        var form = document.querySelector('.email_form');\n\n        if (!input.value) {\n            e.preventDefault();\n            e.stopPropagation();\n            return false;\n        }\n\n        submit.setAttribute('data-original-text', submit.innerText);\n        submit.innerText = submit.getAttribute('data-submit-text');\n        submit.setAttribute('disabled', 'disabled');\n\n        var action = form.getAttribute('action');\n        var emailValue = form.elements.email.value;\n        var tokenValue = form.elements.token.value;\n\n        var fetchOptions = {\n            method: 'POST',\n            credentials: 'include',\n            headers: {\n                'X-Requested-With': 'XMLHttpRequest',\n                'Content-type': 'application/json',\n            },\n            body: JSON.stringify({\n                email: emailValue,\n                token: tokenValue\n            })\n        };\n\n        fetch(action, fetchOptions)\n            .then(function(response) {\n                if (!response.ok) {\n                    throw new Error();\n                }\n                return response.json();\n            })\n            .then(function(json) {\n                if (json.success) {\n                    input.classList.remove('iris_input--error');\n                    submit.innerText = submit.getAttribute('data-submit-success');\n                    submit.classList.add('submitted');\n                }\n                else {\n                    throw new Error();\n                }\n            })\n            .catch(emailSubmissionError);\n\n        return false;\n    }\n\n    function toggleFeatureList(event) {\n        document.querySelector('#feature_list').classList.toggle('hide');\n        document.querySelector('.feature_section_close').classList.toggle('hide');\n    }\n\n    /* global PlayerManager,Signal
